Ports for constructing kde version 4.
Contributions are welcome

How to test this git:

1. Clone it

$ git clone git@github.com/NuTyX/kde.git

2. adjust /etc/cards by adding the ports directory

$ dir /usr/ports/kde

3. create an alias

$ alias sync_kde='cd /home/<youraccount>/kde/;git pull;sudo rsync -av --exclude '.*.swp'  --exclude '*~'  --delete /home/<youraccount>/kde/ /usr/ports/kde/;sudo chown -R 0:0 /usr/ports/kde/'

Add this alias into your ~/.bashrc to make permanent

4. build the ports

$ cards depcreate kde


Have fun :)
